title: 🤩🤩 2 BED 1 BATH 🤩🤩 633 Marcy Ave
posting_body: ['September 1st move in date', 'One month broker fee', 'Text Lihi @ 3477484234 w/ address 633 Marcy', 'Welcome to 633 Marcy Ave! a high end Luxury building, Living at 633 Marcy comes with its perks.', 'You will be living amongst an all inclusive amenities building.', 'Including a state of the art fitness center, bike storage, laundry facilities and of course a fantastic rooftop terrace!', 'Large 2 Bedroom / 1 Bath!', '***3TH FLOOR UNIT WITH GREAT NATURAL LIGHT***', 'With vast windows this unit absorbs a tremendous amount of natural light!!', 'The warmth of the oak wood floors and kitchen cabinets along with the modern appliances are finishes to show off, not to mention the waterfall shower head!', 'UNIT FEATURES Central Air Conditioner - Custom Kitchen & Baths - High Ceilings -Natural', 'Light Oak Finishes - Private Balcony - Slate Countertops - dishwasher Located in Bedstuy at the East Williamsburg, Clinton Hill and Bushwick borders.', 'Just a few minute walk to The Myrtle - Willoughby G train!', 'With the J M Z Flushing Ave and Myrtle Broadway Stop near by.', 'Lincoln Supermarket located on the ground floor!', 'With home depot a block away.', 'Just a few blocks from MM Coffee shop and lots of bars and restaurants in the area!', 'Life just got a little more convenient and a whole lot more comfortable!!']
